title: Rosh hashanah honey cake
ingredients: ['200g (7 oz) caster sugar', '250ml (8 fl oz) honey', '120ml (4 fl oz) vegetable oil', '4 eggs', '2 teaspoons grated orange zest', '250ml (8 fl oz) orange juice', '300g (11 oz) plain flour', '1 tablespoon baking powder', '1/2 teaspoon bicarbonate of soda', '1/2 teaspoon salt', '1 teaspoon ground cinnamon']
